Hey All!  Cards all sold, thanks Guys!


here is a nice lot of 19 cards from the harder to find last series (126 - 150) in the set.   I will sell as priced below.  Pricing is delivered.   Any form of payment is fine.  

All are raw cards and range from poor to VG, some with back damage.  Pictures of the fronts are below.  email me if you would like additional pictures.

thanks!

Cliff
